* Finite state machine for the CD4510
* Counts from 0 to 9, incrementing or decrementing on each clock
* depending on the state of the upd input.
* Does not increment when cin is high.
* When preset is enabled (pen) the counter state is determined by the p inputs
*
* See https://www.ti.com/lit/ds/symlink/cd4510b.pdf for truth table and logic
*
* Allan McInnes / University of Canterbury / 2024-12-10
*
* General format:
* [state#] [outputs] [inputs] -> [next state#]
* q1 q2 q3 q4 cout; upd cin pen p1 p2 p3 p4
0 0s 0s 0s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 1
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 9
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 0
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

1 1s 0s 0s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 2
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 0
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 1
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

2 0s 1s 0s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 3
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 1
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 2
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

3 1s 1s 0s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 4
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 2
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

4 0s 0s 1s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 5
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 3
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 4
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

5 1s 0s 1s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 6
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 4
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 5
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

6 0s 1s 1s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 7
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 5
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 6
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

7 1s 1s 1s 0s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 8
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 6
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

8 0s 0s 0s 1s 1s 1 0 x x x x x -> 9
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 7
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 8
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9

9 1s 0s 0s 1s 0s 1 0 x x x x x -> 0
                 0 0 x x x x x -> 8
                 x 1 x x x x x -> 9
                 x x 1 0 0 0 0 -> 0
                 x x 1 1 0 0 0 -> 1
                 x x 1 0 1 0 0 -> 2
                 x x 1 1 1 0 0 -> 3
                 x x 1 0 0 1 0 -> 4
                 x x 1 1 0 1 0 -> 5
                 x x 1 0 1 1 0 -> 6
                 x x 1 1 1 1 0 -> 7
                 x x 1 0 0 0 1 -> 8
                 x x 1 1 0 0 1 -> 9